### <a id='features'></a> Features

Features included in this release:

- Spring Cloud Data Flow has been updated to SCDF Pro version 1.3.0
- Spring Cloud Skipper has been updated to 2.7.0-M1
- Composed Task Runner 2.8.0-M1 container image is now provided
